Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:34.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  贵志  你来看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.26,0:01:36.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.08,0:01:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我买了这么多零食
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.58,0:01:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很多啊  塔子婶婶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.68,0:01:46.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你带去参加习题合宿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.97,0:01:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.60,0:01:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后这包薯片装不进去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.75,0:02:02.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法  现在就解决了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.71,0:02:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你替别人着想的方式真够笨拙的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.95,0:02:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师你也来帮忙吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.13,0:02:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  老是要人操心
